{"tid":446712,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測) 嚇鬼阿嫂 死亡特訓 自殺特攻","createTime":"2017-10-24T14:22:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-24T17:22:02.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5f609ef5091085632abf7bf23aa7903de24e8aac","tid":446712,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T14:22:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=BE8umleqyV4iKsUKwd3M4%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=849beeee\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> V台入佢主頁睇先比較順<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=BE8umleqyV4iKsUKwd3M4%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=12a4a377\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> dailymotion執柒左 好似係<br />\n<a href=\"https://ok.ru/videoembed/342246366917\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fok.ru%2Fvideoembed%2F342246366917&d=BE8umleqyV4iKsUKwd3M4%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=5775fd0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://ok.ru/videoembed/342246366917</a>全MON版 測試中<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/vi/d/dc/Pee_Mak_International_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fvi%2Fd%2Fdc%2FPee_Mak_International_Poster.jpg&h=ef3c2016&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/danlkaelb/1317574242-405469938.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fdanlkaelb%2F1317574242-405469938.jpg&h=4f93b7ba&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/9/96/Suicide_Squad_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F9%2F96%2FSuicide_Squad_Poster.jpg&h=0fcadd8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.於泰國拉達那哥欣王國期間，小邁（馬力歐&middot;慕瑞 飾）被徵召入軍隊，留下懷孕的妻子小奈（Mai Davika Hoorne 飾），戰爭結束後，他帶同四位戰友小特、老普、阿信、阿艾回到家鄉，與妻子小奈及戰爭期間出世的兒子小特小特重聚。一家人以為又快快樂樂地生活，四位好友亦打算留下當地展開新生活。<br />\n可是不久便傳出小奈原來在小邁征戰期間因難產而死，四位兄弟為了查個明白，便追查謠言源頭，可是發現當事人已被淹死，四人驚覺身邊阿嫂及仔仔原來是鬼魂，下一個受害者可能就是自己！四人猶疑要否告知小邁的真相，可是他們也怕鬼魂滅口，他們如何避過鬼魂追殺，同時又向小邁透露真相......<br />\n<br />\n2.七個年輕FBI特務受訓員，將要進入最後考驗，他們主力研究兇手的犯罪心理模式，要成為FBI內的「獵兇者」，負責最後測試的是高級FBI特務夏利（韋基馬飾），他要七人在一個荒島裡找出連環殺人狂兇&mdash;「木偶法師」。七個組員被送到荒島後，就發現這不單純是一次訓練，因為在他們當中，其中一人就是這個連環殺人狂兇。一次狙兇訓練，竟變成被兇手獵殺的遊戲，生死一線間，各人祇好與時間競賽&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n3.經過超人之死的浩劫後，隸屬政府秘密組織「天眼局」的女官員阿曼達&middot;華勒，決定組織一支由多名極度危險罪犯所組成的「X特遣部隊」，來為美國政府承擔高風險任務，確保有人能夠阻止下一個侵害社會的強大敵人。華勒到美夢監獄招收了多名惡名昭彰的超級罪犯：槍法精準的精英殺手「死亡射手」、瘋狂及致命的前精神科醫生「哈莉&middot;奎茵」、能夠召喚火焰的前洛杉磯幫派分子「燄魔」、善用迴旋鏢的澳洲盜賊「迴旋鏢隊長」、因為基因突變而擁有鱷魚外表和習性的野蠻罪犯「殺手鱷」、以及善用繩索的職業傭兵「繩鬼」，讓他們全部聽從由政府指派的軍官上校瑞克&middot;佛萊格的指揮，而每個人的脖子裏都被注射一顆小型奈米炸彈作為保險措施，以防止他們在任務中造反或是逃跑..<br />\n<br />\n10 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=BE8umleqyV4iKsUKwd3M4%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=614aa3e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=BE8umleqyV4iKsUKwd3M4%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=d773d95f\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af6457cfaacf10a465c2032cd42d55d5204a95f3","tid":446712,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T14:23:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"561cf8c747493bfc720f278d76b4fef7fadfed3e","tid":446712,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T14:32:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c42b52543df383a2e71df748939dca9bfa6aa5f1","tid":446712,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T14:55:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6b5023bc174a62b77f9f502d88caf7ffd6a3be6","tid":446712,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T15:13:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab614b698750e94709dd2dadfbdedb7cbadc7e0d","tid":446712,"uid":89402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T15:13:57.000Z","msg":"有無周星馳啲戲揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"835d62e73b1889d9593118df316bd25c6f5a8c02","tid":446712,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T15:32:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0e0a3065eefc4d82b7c272b20b563ebc9c2944f","tid":446712,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T15:55:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img sr